divs: Sighting DetailsOctober 25th 9:55 pm 2012 We were trying to take photos of Jupiter. Since it was dark my camera (Canon EOS DIGITAL REBEL XTi) used an exposure time of 10 seconds. An airplane flew through the field of view that had solid and flashing lights, which when viewed in the 10 second photo appeared as 2 parallel lines and dots. I am a certified moron, so I thought I would report this as a UFO.
